  "text": "For the first time, we reported the selective PEC oxidation of 5-(hydroxymethyl)-2-furaldehyde to 2,5-furandicarbaldehyde by nanotube structured TiO 2 on Ti layer as photoanodes, prepared by anodic oxidation method in HF medium [CITATION_1] . In addition, the photoanodes were also platinized by photoreduction method and both product selectivity and PEC activity significantly increased.",
